    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface CommonContact
extends gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    This is a shared delegate/interface which allows code to operate on those common properties held by either Contact or ABContact entities. This allows code-sharing in cases where code might be used by both ContactManager and another Guidewire application.
